<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Imported Labour — The Evolution of Immigrant Employment in Canada</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400;1,700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --ink: #1a1209;
    --cream: #f5f0e8;
    --parchment: #e8dfc9;
    --rust: #b84a1e;
    --gold: #c9963a;
    --steel: #3d5a6e;
    --forest: #2d4a35;
    --ash: #6b6259;
    --light-ash: #a89f95;
    --white: #fdfaf5;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ─── NAV ─────────────────────────────── */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: var(--ink);
    padding: 0 2rem;
    height: 52px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  nav .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  nav ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  nav ul a {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--light-ash);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  nav ul a:hover { color: var(--cream); }

  /* ─── HERO ────────────────────────────── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding-top: 52px;
    background: var(--ink);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-texture {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      repeating-linear-gradient(
        0deg,
        transparent,
        transparent 2px,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.015) 2px,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.015) 3px
      );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 6rem 4rem 6rem 5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .hero-tag {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rust);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .hero-tag::before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 2rem;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--rust);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 6vw, 6rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.0;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--light-ash);
    max-width: 440px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .hero-byline {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--ash);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .hero-right {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .hero-visual {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .timeline-spine {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 15%;
    bottom: 15%;
    width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--gold) 20%, var(--gold) 80%, transparent);
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }

  .era-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gold);
    border: 2px solid var(--ink);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .era-dot::after {
    content: attr(data-label);
    position: absolute;
    left: 1.5rem;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--ash);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .era-dot:nth-child(2) { top: 18%; }
  .era-dot:nth-child(3) { top: 34%; }
  .era-dot:nth-child(4) { top: 50%; }
  .era-dot:nth-child(5) { top: 66%; }
  .era-dot:nth-child(6) { top: 82%; }

  /* ─── SCROLL INDICATOR ─── */
  .scroll-hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    animation: bounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .scroll-hint span {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--ash);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .scroll-arrow {
    width: 1px;
    height: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--ash), transparent);
  }
  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(6px); }
  }

  /* ─── INTRO THESIS ─── */
  .thesis-section {
    background: var(--parchment);
    padding: 7rem 5rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .thesis-label {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rust);
    padding-top: 0.5rem;
    position: sticky;
    top: 6rem;
  }

  .thesis-body blockquote {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
  }

  .thesis-body p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #3d3328;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  /* ─── CHAPTER SECTIONS ─── */
  .chapter {
    padding: 7rem 5rem;
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .chapter:nth-child(odd) { background: var(--white); }
  .chapter:nth-child(even) { background: var(--cream); }

  .chapter-header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--parchment);
  }

  .chapter-number {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--parchment);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .chapter:nth-child(even) .chapter-number {
    color: rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
  }

  .chapter-meta {}
  .chapter-era {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rust);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .chapter-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .chapter-subtitle {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--ash);
    max-width: 600px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .chapter-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .chapter-body.reverse { grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr; }
  .chapter-body.reverse .chapter-text { order: 2; }
  .chapter-body.reverse .chapter-aside { order: 1; }

  .chapter-text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: #2e2820;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .chapter-aside {}

  .stat-card {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--cream);
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .stat-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 3px;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--gold);
  }
  .stat-number {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--light-ash);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .stat-note {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--ash);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .pull-quote {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--rust);
    background: var(--parchment);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .pull-quote p {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .pull-quote cite {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--ash);
    font-style: normal;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ─── DARK CHAPTER (CPR) ─── */
  .chapter.dark-chapter {
    background: var(--ink);
  }
  .chapter.dark-chapter .chapter-number { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
  .chapter.dark-chapter .chapter-era { color: var(--rust); }
  .chapter.dark-chapter .chapter-title { color: var(--cream); }
  .chapter.dark-chapter .chapter-subtitle { color: var(--light-ash); }
  .chapter.dark-chapter .chapter-header { border-bottom-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  .chapter.dark-chapter .chapter-text p { color: #c8bfb4; }
  .chapter.dark-chapter .pull-quote {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-left-color: var(--gold);
  }
  .chapter.dark-chapter .pull-quote p { color: var(--cream); }
  .chapter.dark-chapter .pull-quote cite { color: var(--ash); }
  .chapter.dark-chapter .stat-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }
  .chapter.dark-chapter .stat-card::before { background: var(--rust); }
  .chapter.dark-chapter .chapter-body { border: none; }

  /* ─── VISUAL TIMELINE BAR ─── */
  .timeline-bar {
    background: var(--ink);
    padding: 4rem 5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .timeline-bar h2 {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ash);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .timeline-track {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 0;
    height: 120px;
  }
  .timeline-track::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }
  .timeline-event {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 0 0.5rem;
    position: relative;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .timeline-event::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0.5rem;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gold);
  }
  .event-year {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .event-desc {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--ash);
    line-height: 1.4;
    padding-bottom: 1.2rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .timeline-event:hover .event-desc {
    color: var(--cream);
    border-bottom-color: var(--rust);
  }

  /* ─── INTERACTIVE QUIZ ─── */
  .quiz-section {
    background: var(--steel);
    padding: 7rem 5rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .quiz-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .quiz-intro {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .quiz-container {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    padding: 3rem;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .quiz-step { display: none; }
  .quiz-step.active { display: block; }

  .quiz-question {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .quiz-options {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .quiz-option {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    transition: all 0.2s;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .quiz-option:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
    color: var(--white);
    border-color: var(--gold);
  }
  .quiz-option.selected {
    background: rgba(201,150,58,0.2);
    border-color: var(--gold);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .quiz-next {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--ink);
    border: none;
    padding: 0.85rem 2.5rem;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
    display: none;
  }
  .quiz-next:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
  .quiz-next.visible { display: inline-block; }

  .quiz-result {
    display: none;
  }
  .quiz-result.active {
    display: block;
  }

  .result-era {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .result-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .result-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 580px;
  }
  .result-verdict {
    background: rgba(184,74,30,0.25);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--rust);
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .quiz-restart {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--light-ash);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .quiz-restart:hover {
    color: var(--white);
    border-color: var(--white);
  }

  /* ─── SOURCES ─── */
  .sources-section {
    background: var(--parchment);
    padding: 6rem 5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  .sources-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .source-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
  }
  .source-item {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--white);
    border-top: 2px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .source-num {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--rust);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .source-citation {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: #3d3328;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .source-type {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--light-ash);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* ─── CONCEPTS ─── */
  .concepts-section {
    background: var(--forest);
    padding: 5rem 5rem;
    color: var(--cream);
  }
  .concepts-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }
  .concept-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  }
  .concept-type {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .concept-name {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .concept-desc {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
  footer {
    background: var(--ink);
    padding: 3rem 5rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  footer .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--cream);
  }
  footer .footer-meta {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    color: var(--ash);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-align: right;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* ─── UTILITY ─── */
  .section-tag {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rust);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .section-tag::before {
    content: '';
    width: 1.5rem;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--rust);
  }

  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
    margin: 3rem 0;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-right { display: none; }
    .thesis-section, .chapter { padding: 4rem 2rem; }
    .thesis-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .chapter-body, .chapter-body.reverse { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .chapter-body.reverse .chapter-text { order: 1; }
    .chapter-body.reverse .chapter-aside { order: 2; }
    .source-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .concepts-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    nav ul { display: none; }
    .timeline-bar { padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    .quiz-section { padding: 4rem 2rem; }
    .sources-section { padding: 4rem 2rem; }
    .concepts-section { padding: 4rem 2rem; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; text-align: center; }
    footer .footer-meta { text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">Imported Labour</div>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#intro">Overview</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ch1">Railways</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ch2">Prairies</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ch3">Points System</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ch4">Today</a></li>
    <li><a href="#quiz">Activity</a></li>
    <li><a href="#sources">Sources</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-texture"></div>
  <div class="hero-left">
    <div class="hero-tag">Grade 11 Interdisciplinary Final Project · Canadian History & English</div>
    <h1>Imported<br><em>Labour</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">The Evolution of Immigrant Employment in Canada — from the railway camps of 1881 to the credential recognition crisis of 2025, Canada has always needed immigrant labour. The question is whether it ever truly valued it.</p>
